Getting started takes just a few minutes.

**Step 1: Bring your email to Fastmail**=20=20
[Use our migration tool](https://app.fastmail.com/settings/migration/import=
) to import your email, contacts, and calendars from your old provider. You=
 can also send and receive from your old address right inside Fastmail.

**Step 2: Get the Fastmail app**=20=20
[Download Fastmail](https://app.fastmail.com/settings/migration/apps) on yo=
ur phone or tablet for push notifications and quick access on the go. We al=
so have [great apps for Mac, Windows, and Linux](https://www.fastmail.com/d=
ownload/).

**Step 3: Make Fastmail yours**=20=20
[Explore your settings](https://app.fastmail.com/settings) to set up your c=
alendars, choose your color scheme, and organize with labels or folders.

All the best,=20=20
The Fastmail Team

